Description: Isn’t being a kid hard enough? For this group, who are also part bird, nothing comes easy.
Title: MAXIMUM RIDE, VOL. 6
Author: James Patterson

Description: Yuma Tsukumo will stop at nothing to become the Duel Masters champion, but as a rank amateur, the odds are stacked against him. Luckily, he has a mysterious spirit named Astral to help him.
Title: YU-GI-OH! ZEXAL, VOL. 2
Author: Kazuki Takahashi

Description: This is not your typical wonderland: Peter is a man with rabbit ears and Elliott March, the Mad Hatter’s enforcer, is a mafia hitman. How will Alice survive?
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF HEARTS: MY FANATIC RABBIT, VOL. 1
Author: Quinrose

Description: Are the magical dreams of Madoka Kaname suddenly becoming a reality?
Title: PUELLA MAGI MADOKA MAGICA, VOL. 3
Author: Magica Quartet

Description: Oz, who is condemned to an abyss for a mysterious sin, sets out to investigate with an Alice, an equally mysterious girl he met in exile.
Title: PANDORA HEARTS, VOL. 13
Author: Jun Mochizuki

Description: Alita is a powerful cyborg with a soft heart and a mysterious past.
Title: BATTLE ANGEL ALITA: LAST ORDER, VOL. 16
Author: Yukito Kishiro

Description: This series is about grade-school boys who want to become professionals in the manga industry.
Title: BAKUMAN, VOL. 17
Author: Tsugumi Ohba

Description: Misao Harada can see into a magical realm where she is the bride demon of prophecy.
Title: BLACK BIRD, VOL. 15
Author: Kanoko Sakurakouji

Description: Naruto and his allies battle an army of undead ninjas and an unexpected resurrection throws them all for a loop.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 59
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume, Ichigo is still on his quest to regain his powers.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 52
Author: Tite Kubo
